name: applicationinsights
description: Microsoft Application Insights module for Node.js

scripts.build: npm run build:deps && npm run build:compile
scripts.test: npm run test:ts && npm run test:js
scripts.functionaltest: npm run build && npm pack && node --use_strict ./Tests/FunctionalTests/RunFunctionalTests.js
scripts.backcompattest: npm run build && npm pack && node --use_strict ./Tests/BackCompatibility/RunBackCompatTests.js
